creator: Clayton Industries
descriptionHtml:
Access your 5k and junior results history and the latest results for each event world wide. Simply enter your barcode and all your results are at your fingertips

Run History


Check out yours and others event history. Keep track of PB's, events you've attended, volunteer roles you've fulfilled and positions you've finished in

Challenges


We've got loads of those, from the ever popular parkrunner alphabet to stopwatch bingo there's something for every parkrunner

Course Info


Looking for a new event to attend? See the location of every event in the world along with directions on how to get there. Read the course description, see a detailed map of the run route and check for cancellations

Volunteering


All parkruns are run by volunteers so we've made volunteering easy. Simply pick an event, view the list of available roles and quickly send an email to the event organiser

Permissions


The camera and or location permissions do not need to be accepted if you do not wish to use the below features

* The camera permission is only required if you wish to scan barcodes when adding new users
* The location permission is only required if you wish to see your current location relative to the location of nearby parkruns

* This is a third party app and is in no way associated with the parkrun Group. parkrun is a registered trademark of parkrun Limited
